race.comment: HURSTVILLE ZAGREB (1) had to work hard from the awkward draw when up in trip and grade for a tiring fourth over 1800m at Rosehill. Can take control here from the inside gate and no excuses fourth-up. LET'S FLY (7) best showing this time in when out to her preferred trip for a fighting nose second over 1800m at Rosehill. Two of her three wins have come at this course and the booking of Braith Nock is a positive. Among the leading chances. OCEANFRONT (2) undefeated in three starts this campaign and shapes as a worthy contender in this stronger race. Rounded them up effortlessly over 1800m at Randwick last time. Can tag the speed and looks great each way value. BRAVE CALL (8) had mixed luck in three starts back and the blinkers go on for this in an attempt to sharpen him up. Berry stays aboard and look for him late. NATOYA (12) progressive mare deep into her prep and ready for this trip. Blinkers come off and no shock to see her take this out.
